<ul><li>Have a half-life which is <b>stable enough</b>&nbsp;for the necessary measurements to be made, and</li><li><b>Short enough</b>&nbsp;to decay quickly after use.<br></li><li>Emit&nbsp;\(\beta\)&nbsp;or&nbsp;\(\gamma\)&nbsp;radiation so it can be<b> detected outside </b>the flow path.</li></ul>